&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;18.75 Hours per week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excellent opportunity for an Occupational Therapist interested and committed to rehabilitation in the community.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic Occupational Therapist to join our team within Middlesbrough Reablement Unit. This is a 15 bedded unit where patient receive rehabilitation in order to return to their normal place of residence, the team consists of Physiotherapists, Occupational Therapists and rehabilitation assistants. The team work very closely with the care staff from Aster Care Home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The service is delivered 5 days a week (Monday to Friday).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sarah Clifford (Community Therapy Team Lead)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
